quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  50,16,We created man and We know what his own self whispers to him. We are nearer to him than his jugular vein
  50,17,"And the two recording angels are recording, sitting on the right and on the left"
  50,18,"He does not utter a single word, without a watcher by him, pen in hand"
  50,19,The throes of death come revealing the truth. That is what you were trying to evade
  50,20,The Trumpet will be blown. That is the Day of the Threat
  50,21,Every self will come together with a driver and a witness
  50,22,´You were heedless of this so We have stripped you of your covering and today your sight is sharp.´
  50,23,"His inseparable comrade will say, ´This is what I have ready for you.´"
  50,24,´Hurl into Hell every obdurate kafir
  50,25,"impeder of good, doubt-causing aggressor"
  50,26,who set up another god together with Allah. Hurl him into the terrible punishment.´
  50,27,"His inseparable comrade will say, ´Our Lord, I did not make him overstep the limits. He was, in any case, far astray.´"
  50,28,"He will say, ´Do not argue in My presence when I gave you advance warning of the Threat"
  50,29,"My Word, once given, is not subject to change and I do not wrong My slaves.´"
  50,30,"On the Day He says to Hell, ´Are you full?´ it will ask, ´Are there no more to come?´"
  50,31,"And the Garden will be brought up close to those with taqwa, not far away"
  50,32,´This is what you were promised. It is for every careful penitent
  50,33,those who fear the All-Merciful in the Unseen and come with a contrite heart
  50,34,Enter it in peace. This is the Day of Timeless Eternity.´
  50,35,They will have there everything they want and with Us there is still more